data.description: Investment opportunity: AS-IS!!!!!! 4-bed, 2.5-bath Yukon, OK house. Turnkey, 2338 sq. ft., 1999 build, 1 acre, 3-car garage. Plumbing, electrical, roof (5 yrs old), HVAC, and foundation sound. Brick fireplace. Ideal for long-term tenants or serene living. 20 mins from Oklahoma City. Great portfolio addition.
